description.text:
Derived from the XO-1 viewfinder. <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.thingiverse.com/thing:330" >http://www.thingiverse.com/thing:330</a> &quot;This is a viewfinder that plugs into the USB slot of an OLPC XO laptop to help kids align the forward-facing camera.&quot;  
The XO-4 has a different USB port configuration than the XO-1. I modified the original .STL file to reflect the changed port arrangement so this Thing would work with the XO-4.  
This thing was made with Tinkercad. Edit it online <a rel="nofollow" href="https://tinkercad.com/things/2SmRiO7mPlN" >https://tinkercad.com/things/2SmRiO7mPlN</a>
